intent: |
  Project glossary stays canonical: new terms from this week's tickets and transcripts are defined;
  conflicting definitions are reconciled in one page.

scope: |
  Project glossary stays canonical: new terms from this week's tickets and transcripts are defined;
  conflicting definitions are reconciled in one page.

summary: |
  Project glossary stays canonical: new terms from this week's tickets and transcripts are defined;
  conflicting definitions are reconciled in one page.

methodology_refs:
